    "description": "War!<br />\r\nWhat is it good for? Absolutely nothing! Unless, of course, you're a weapon's merchant.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAlchemist of War is a casual card game with crafting elements.<br />\r\nPlay as the Alchemist Merchant. Craft weapons using random ingredients.<br />\r\nYour customers are from both sides of a war. But you don't have any favorites! As long as they keep paying. And if the fight goes on longer, maybe you can sell more.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeaturing:<br />\r\n15 different weapons<br />\r\n15 crafting ingredient cards<br />\r\n11 unique customers<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTry to reach a higher score by balancing the power between the warring factions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHey, They're gonna fight anyway, right?... Right??",
